Print a 'ncdump -h' command

Source: R/ncdump.R
ncdump.Rd

Read a NetCDF and print the medatada

Usage

ncdump(file = file.choose())

Arguments

file

file name

Value

No return value, only display information

Examples

ncdump(file = paste0(system.file("extdata",package="eva3dm"),
                     '/wrfinput_d01'))
